5. Scope

AutoLake focuses on generating normalized Lakehouse artifacts from semi-structured data that has already been ingested into the Lakehouse.

The system covers:

* Source-repository analysis
* Lakehouse-ingestion analysis
* Schema extraction
* Entity and relationship discovery
* Relational-model generation
* PURE model generation
* Materialized-view generation
* Validation and review
* GitLab branch and merge-request creation

The current solution does not aim to replace the complete data-ingestion platform. It works after the source data has been onboarded or when the corresponding ingestion configuration is available.

